AI 
  teaches computers to do things that normally require human intelligence. Businesses leverage AI and ML to add intelligence to their applications and leverage trends(tendencias) and patterns in data.

Rekognition
  It allows you to:
    automate your image and video analysis.
    Identify custom labels in images and videos
    Face and text detection in image and videos

Comprehend 
  It is a natural-language processing (NLP) service that finds relationships in text.
  It uncovers insights and relationships
  Ex:
    You can use comprehend to review social media posts, to detect words and make sentimantal analysis.It a great way to analyse the satisfaction of your customers.

Polly
  It turns text into speech. 
  It mimics natural-sounding human speech. 
  It has several voices across many languages 
  It can create custom voices.

  EX:
    Polly could convert the text on a blog post to speech that could then be downloaded or replayed in MP3 format. Audio is often a great complement to written communication.

SageMaker
  Helps you build, train, and deploy machine learning models quickly.
  Prepare data for models 
  Train and deploy models
  Provides Deep Learning AMIs
  EX:
    Companies like Netflix and Amaxon use ML models to recommend movies and products to buy. SageMaker is a great tool for creating these models.

Translate
  Provides language translation
  Provides real-rime and batch language translation 
  translate many content formats
  Ex:
    Translate allows you to add localization to your application to support your diverse user base. Translate supports several populaar languages. 

Lex
  Helps you build conversational interfaces like chatbots. 
  Recongnizes speech and understands languages.
  Build highly engaging chatbots.
  It powers Amazon Alexa.

  Ex:
    Amazon used the same technologies that power Lex to integrate Amazon Alexa with the device.
